<br />\n你直去pattaya都好d，曼谷市區日日都大塞車</blockquote><br />\n我就係拎完車直去芭堤雅<br />\n回程就早一日返bkk還車先<br />\n當晚係曼谷就坐bts，因為都聽話曼谷渣車不智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，坐bts果陣見到下面d車龍都覺得誇張<br />\n<br />\n你唔好揀返工／放工時間返去還車，我驚入市區果陣都塞到你喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於架車d制，識打燈轉波落hand break，再調好d鏡就應該夠（好似係）"},{"pid":"05e9890ed5f405305e3ecdec258bdae845254188","tid":44184,"uid":22655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:32:13.000Z","msg":"點解唔包車呢？方便好多"},{"pid":"330e83155a38c0cb8707d41c5099c5849cc365af","tid":44184,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔包車呢？方便好多</blockquote><br />\n我知係方便，享受下揸車既樂趣麻"},{"pid":"19c5d66fc6869ec2c15bbd24b846723fbeca7b48","tid":44184,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>泰國都係右駄，拎完車係停車場兜幾個圈練下都得，最緊要熟架車既性能<br />\n<br />\n你直去pattaya都好d，曼谷市區日日都大塞車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n租左jazz<br />\n我係怕到時唔記得d掣係邊個打邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到還？ 要留意唔係全部油站都岩你既油<br />\nJazz 既油叫 E20綠色字 ， 入油站前 望下個牌有無"},{"pid":"0c08c439fdb7b16f744a9efea985efdd808bf498","tid":44184,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔包車呢？方便好多</blockquote><br />\n我知係方便，享受下揸車既樂趣麻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncut 線 要快狠準 <br />\nPattaya 條路120km/h 自己小心d"},{"pid":"cc3a4e03621ae824bd38f447c1639177dad6f69e","tid":44184,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泰國都係右駄，拎完車係停車場兜幾個圈練下都得，最緊要熟架車既性能<br />\n<br />\n你直去pattaya都好d，曼谷市區日日都大塞車</blockquote><br />\n我就係拎完車直去芭堤雅<br />\n回程就早一日返bkk還車先<br />\n當晚係曼谷就坐bts，因為都聽話曼谷渣車不智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，坐bts果陣見到下面d車龍都覺得誇張<br />\n<br />\n你唔好揀返工／放工時間返去還車，我驚入市區果陣都塞到你喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於架車d制，識打燈轉波落hand break，再調好d鏡就應該夠（好似係）</blockquote><br />\n我學個陣係棍<br />\n其實自動波由P波到我想行車係咪要踩住迫力先可以轉D波<br />\n跟住先放手掣行車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未渣過自動<br />\n跟住如果係燈位停低係咪踩實迫力就可以唔駛轉P<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084a627ae92c26c73e6b172e7325410edd37aaff","tid":44184,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:41:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泰國都係右駄，拎完車係停車場兜幾個圈練下都得，最緊要熟架車既性能<br />\n<br />\n你直去pattaya都好d，曼谷市區日日都大塞車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n租左jazz<br />\n我係怕到時唔記得d掣係邊個打邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到還？ 要留意唔係全部油站都岩你既油<br />\nJazz 既油叫 E20綠色字 ， 入油站前 望下個牌有無</blockquote><br />\n都係番bkk機場還"},{"pid":"115ff5aa54aa0348c8d4c3d1058fd1ab0a2dc55c","tid":44184,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解唔包車呢？方便好多</blockquote><br />\n我知係方便，享受下揸車既樂趣麻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncut 線 要快狠準 <br />\nPattaya 條路120km/h 自己小心d</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打提醒"},{"pid":"c6d7a21f714cffd73e15d9d0ccadaea839935232","tid":44184,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n租左jazz<br />\n我係怕到時唔記得d掣係邊個打邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊到還？ 要留意唔係全部油站都岩你既油<br />\nJazz 既油叫 E20綠色字 ， 入油站前 望下個牌有無</blockquote><br />\n都係番bkk機場還</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nShell Montien Rung Rueng Branch 1<br />\nGoogle map下 <br />\n全部還車都係附近"},{"pid":"aff7ad5c8e0249351352a4082f134a261d40869f","tid":44184,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquo